    <article id="main-content" class="article">
      <header class="article-header">
        <h1 title="How to Buy ATLAS and POLIS Tokens" class="article-title">
          How to Buy ATLAS and POLIS Tokens
          
        </h1>

        <div class="article-author">
          
          <div class="article-meta">
            

            <div class="meta-group">
              
                <span class="meta-data"><time datetime="2025-12-08T18:23:22Z" title="2025-12-08T18:23:22Z" data-datetime="relative">December 08, 2025 18:23</time></span>
                <span class="meta-data">Updated</span>
              
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        
          <div class="article-subscribe"><div data-helper="subscribe" data-json="{&quot;item&quot;:&quot;article&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;/hc/en-us/articles/47061462878355-How-to-Buy-ATLAS-and-POLIS-Tokens/subscription.json&quot;,&quot;follow_label&quot;:&quot;Follow&quot;,&quot;unfollow_label&quot;:&quot;Unfollow&quot;,&quot;following_label&quot;:&quot;Following&quot;,&quot;can_subscribe&quot;:true,&quot;is_subscribed&quot;:false}"></div></div>
        
      </header>

      <section class="article-info">
        <div class="article-content">
          <div class="article-body"><p>Star Atlas's in-game currencies are easy to buy using a credit card or by swapping other crypto tokens.</p><h3 id="h_01KBJN2VH6YZ93CZPW99C3SCJQ">What Are ATLAS and POLIS?</h3><ul>
<li><p><strong>ATLAS</strong> is the main currency used for gameplay buy ships, resources, crew, and more.</p></li>
<li><p><strong>POLIS</strong> is the governance token lock it to vote in the DAO and earn POLIS rewards.</p></li>
</ul><p>Both tokens are built on the <strong>Solana blockchain</strong>, so you’ll need a <strong>Solana wallet</strong> (like <a target="_new" rel="noopener">Phantom</a>) to hold and use them in Star Atlas.</p><h3 id="h_01KBJN2VH6TS7QZ1TNJFGV7M79">Buy with a Credit Card on PLAY</h3><p>You can buy ATLAS, POLIS, or SOL directly from your wallet section on <a href="https://play.staratlas.com" target="_new" rel="noopener">play.staratlas.com</a> using <strong>Topper</strong>, a fiat on-ramp provider.</p><h4 id="h_01KBJN20M1MTFR09TEGJHQQBGJ">How it works:</h4><ol>
<li><p>Open the wallet panel on PLAY</p></li>
<li><p>Scroll down to <strong>"Manage your wallet’s funds"</strong></p></li>
<li><p>Click <strong>Launch</strong> next to <em><em>Topper</em></em></p></li>
<li>
<p>In the popup:</p>
<ul>
<li><p>Select your currency (USD, EUR, etc.)</p></li>
<li><p>Choose <strong>ATLAS</strong>, <strong>POLIS</strong>, or <strong>SOL</strong></p></li>
<li><p>Enter your payment details and complete KYC</p></li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol><p>Once approved, the tokens will be sent to your wallet.</p><p>📝 <em><em>Note: You can use the tokens right away in SAGE or the Marketplace.</em></em></p><h3 id="h_01KBJN2VH6SFDWA7RNNEH8RSQA">Swap Tokens on a DEX (Decentralized Exchange)</h3><p>If your wallet already holds <strong>SOL</strong> or <strong>USDC</strong>, you can use a decentralized exchange like:</p><ul>
<li><p><a href="https://jup.ag" target="_new" rel="noopener">Jupiter Aggregator</a> (recommended)</p></li>
<li><p><a href="https://raydium.io" target="_new" rel="noopener">Raydium</a></p></li>
<li><p><a href="https://orca.so" target="_new" rel="noopener">Orca</a></p></li>
</ul><p>Just connect your wallet, choose the token you want to swap (e.g. SOL → ATLAS), and confirm the transaction.</p><h3 id="h_01KBJN2VH6HWAZTWCT7YF4PJXX">Buy on a Centralized Exchange (CEX)</h3><p>ATLAS and POLIS are also available on centralized exchanges like:</p><ul>
<li><p><a href="https://www.gate.com/trade/POLIS_USDT" rel="noopener">Gate.io</a></p></li>
<li><p><a href="https://www.mexc.com/exchange/POLIS_USDT" rel="noopener">MEXC</a></p></li>
<li><p><a href="https://pro.kraken.com/app/trade/polis-eur" rel="noopener">Kraken</a></p></li>
</ul><p>On these platforms, you can:</p><ul>
<li><p>Create an account</p></li>
<li><p>Deposit funds (like USDT or USD)</p></li>
<li><p>Buy ATLAS or POLIS</p></li>
<li><p>Send your tokens to your Solana wallet</p></li>
</ul><h3 id="h_01KBJN20M1FMSKT28AFX7X2Z8Y">Summary: 3 Ways to Buy</h3><div><div><table style="border-collapse: collapse;  margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; border: 1px solid #99acc2; width: 100%; height: 119px;">
<thead><tr>
<th style="width: 33.2849%;" data-col-size="sm">Method</th>
<th style="width: 33.2849%;" data-col-size="sm">Use Case</th>
<th style="width: 33.2849%;" data-col-size="sm">Tools</th>
</tr></thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td style="width: 33.2849%; text-align: center;" data-col-size="sm">Credit Card</td>
<td style="width: 33.2849%; text-align: center;" data-col-size="sm">Fastest &amp; easiest for new users</td>
<td style="width: 33.2849%; text-align: center;" data-col-size="sm">Topper on play.staratlas.com</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="width: 33.2849%; text-align: center;" data-col-size="sm">Swap</td>
<td style="width: 33.2849%; text-align: center;" data-col-size="sm">If you already have SOL or USDC</td>
<td style="width: 33.2849%; text-align: center;" data-col-size="sm">Jupiter, Raydium, Orca</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="width: 33.2849%; text-align: center;" data-col-size="sm">Centralized Exchange</td>
<td style="width: 33.2849%; text-align: center;" data-col-size="sm">For traders or fiat-to-crypto conversion</td>
<td style="width: 33.2849%; text-align: center;" data-col-size="sm">Gate.io, MEXC, Kraken</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table></div></div></div>

          

          
        </div>
      </section>

